The “L-ambush” as a defensive pattern

Don’t challenge along the main axis (“is it valid?”).
Add a side-angle check:
	•	Why now? (timing)
	•	Why this actor/device? (context)
	•	Why this jump in power? (proportionality)
	•	Does the story match the mechanics? (narrative vs reality)

If two of those disagree → pause, step-up verify, or isolate.

